https://www.trading-logic.com</a><br />\ntradeview version<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tradingview.com/script/Z80gO0Ny/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tradingview.com%2Fscript%2FZ80gO0Ny%2F&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=a39d06e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tradingview.com/script/Z80gO0Ny/</a><br />\nARK 追蹤神器<br />\n<a href=\"https://ark.alien-tomato.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fark.alien-tomato.com&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=4a083d2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://ark.alien-tomato.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9af01ys.png&amp;h=2794d7b6&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\">《方舟投資主禱文》<br />\n我們在天上的母：願人都尊契媽的名為聖。<br />\n願契媽的國降臨，願契媽的電動車馳騁在地上，<br />\n如同爆升在天上。我們盼望的升幅，<br />\n求契媽今日賜給我們，又求饒恕石仔拋售的罪，<br />\n因為我們饒恕得罪SH的人。<br />\n不叫我們遇見破壞性創新，拯救我們脫離短炒。<br />\n離開方舟的叛徒，定必受到地獄之火的懲罰。<br />\n因為坐貨、賺錢、移民，<br />\n全是契媽的子民，直到永遠。阿們。</span></p><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpyrcfjq.gif&amp;h=9f6bf1e8&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\nTrello 開左Public美股認真討論區 board，慢慢搬野上去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F513A9wIT&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=85377385\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT</a><br />\n<br />\n開左個美股認真討論區（全民編輯留言區），巴打可以加野上去，周末有空會整理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/1SNId2E3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F1SNId2E3&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=d9c50ada\" target=\"_blank\"